entityTypeAndLegalNameIntro: Enter your entity type and the legal name of your company. You can find this info on your <einLink>FEIN assignment form (Form CP575)</einLink>. We need this to file and pay your taxes correctly.
federalEinDescription: Your company's Federal Employer Identification Number (EIN). If you don't have one, please <applyLink>apply online.</applyLink>
taxpayerTypeDescription: Some common types are Sole Prop, LLC, and S-Corp.
federalFilingFormDescription: To learn more about the different Federal Tax Form filings for payroll, please review the <irsLink>IRS website.</irsLink>
legalEntityNameDescription: Make sure this is the legal name of the company, not your DBA.
